      "position": "Scrum-half",
      "nationality": "Wales",
      "blurb": "Gloucester's 2025-26 club captain and reigning Premiership Rugby Player of the Season; 69-cap Wales 9 and 2025 Lions tourist who scored twice against the Western Force in Perth before a hamstring injury cut his tour short. A sniping running threat, sharp service and tempo control from the base — confirmed in December 2025 to be joining Saracens at season's end",
